        <!-- ===== LEGEND ===== -->
        <mxCell id="legend" value="LEGEND&#10;Nodes:  ◼ SR OS PE (Nokia)   ◼ SR Linux P   ◼ IOS-XR PE (Cisco)   ◼ Transit (CSR/IOL)   ◼ IXP / FRR   ◼ FortiGate CE   ◼ Aruba LAN   ◼ IOSv spare   ◼ RPKI/Routinator   ◻ Workloads&#10;Links:  ── IS-IS L2 + LDP    ─ ─ iBGP VPNv4 (full mesh)    ── eBGP transit    ── IXP eBGP (L2 fabric)    ─ ─→ RS-reflected (LP 300)    ─ ─→ RPKI-RTR    ··· workload LAN&#10;Policy:  LOCAL_PREF  IXP 300 &gt; Transit-A 200 &gt; Transit-B 100   ·   reject RPKI-Invalid at edge   ·   no transit→IXP leak   ·   max-prefix per transit   ·   ROV target = every eBGP ingress (Phase C1 XR-only → C3 all)&#10;Build phases:  A) IPv4 BGP fabric  →  B) IPv6 dual-stack  →  C) RPKI/ROV     |     Lab-only: doc ASNs/prefixes + SLURM VRPs — never advertised to the real Internet" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#fafafa;strokeColor=#bdbdbd;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
